About Us

 

Eco Mobile Bike Repair (EMBR) is a small company run by Austin Chamney, a mechanic of 4 year's experience at re-Cycles community bike shop.

EMBR's goal is to provide professional mechanical service in a convenient and affordable manner. The hope is that this will encourage fellow Ottawa citizens to get outside and enjoy the fresh air.

Why Eco?

It would seem like a shame to service eco-friendly bikes with a not-so-eco-friendly vehicle, so only an electric service vehicle will do! I show up at your door using the power of the sun.
